<subSubSection id="3B4792BF7D4205427874151D3CAFAA6B" pageId="1" pageNumber="54" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="5F2A642BD3A0920ABE52EC40972C83DB" pageId="1" pageNumber="54">Distribution, habitat and ecology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1A38DD444D95BC6E820C48C11EA3B61A" pageId="1" pageNumber="54">Endemic to Vanuatu where it occurs as an uncommon epiphyte on the bark of tree trunks and branches in the canopy to subcanopy of mature trees in lowland to montane primary tropical rainforest.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
